## Email Fulfillment

### Short term
`{{layout handle="sales_email_order_items_tracking" order=$order}}`
Inform customer about how many products(qty) that will deliver on this shipment.

### Shipment Tracking
`{{layout handle="sales_email_order_shipment_tracking" shipment=$shipment order=$order}}`
Inform customer about how many products that are already delivered (0, if it's not delivered yet)